    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs super smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you\u2019re getting a dependable car that's ready to hit the road today. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
