      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. The exterior, finished in a deep Obsidian Black, retains a high-gloss luster, showing only minor, expected road wear such as small stone chips on the front fascia. Step inside to a smoke-free cabin where the pebble-gray leather seats remain supple; the driver\u2019s bolster shows slight softening, but the interior overall is remarkably clean and well-preserved. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive log included. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the suspension remains taut and quiet over bumps. Recent updates include a fresh set of all-season tires and a new battery. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between a brand-new showroom model and a seasoned daily driver.",
